# Leaderboard Queries

## Objective
Create the database queries to establish user and clan rankings.

## Tasks
1. Write a query to fetch the top global users ordered by level then XP.
2. Write a query to compute clan rankings based on the aggregate XP of their members.
3. Expose these functions safely to authenticated users.
